description: Brand new 1 BED at the newest condominium development in South Boston, Vesta! Recently completed this year, amenities include a common roof deck with Boston skyline views, a top floor clubroom w/ a wet bar and an outdoor pet play area. Vesta is a professionally managed elevator building.  408 features high end finishes including Carrara Quartz countertops and backsplashes, Metropolitan cabinetry, Bosch kitchen appliances including gas cooking, 'vented' in-unit washers and dryers and Kahrs Life Collection hardwood flooring.  The luxuriously appointed bathroom includes Ultra White Quartz countertops, Porcelanosa shower tiles and flooring and Moen faucets. Vesta retail will include include Bell's Grocery Market and cafe. Bell's will offer daily conveniences such as groceries, prepared foods and wine/beer and is expected to open later this Summer.  408 is ready for immediate occupancy
